I"<<p>Zimbabwe fought a bitter struggle to gain independence from settler colonialism. In this episode, I discuss the political economy of the liberation struggle with academic and farmer Cde Benny Moyo.</p>

<p>Intro music is “Toputika Neshungu” by Mbira DzeNharira. Outro is “Love and scandals” by Solomon Skuza.</p>

<p>Article image is ‘a bush training base’ during the liberation struggle. Image credit The Herald.</p>

